Enum Class HumanoidArm

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<net.minecraft.world.entity.HumanoidArm>
net.minecraft.world.entity.HumanoidArm
public enum HumanoidArm extends Enum<HumanoidArm>
Represents a Player's Arm, either HumanoidArm#LEFT or HumanoidArm#RIGHT.
